longBusinessSummary: Trastor Real Estate Investment Company SA operates as a property investment company in Greece. Its property portfolio includes shops, offices, gas stations, and garages. The company was formerly known as Piraeus Real Estate Investment Company and changed its name to Trastor Real Estate Investment Company SA in May 2009. Trastor Real Estate Investment Company is headquartered in Athens, Greece. Trastor Real Estate Investment Company SA (ATSE:TRASTOR) operates as a subsidiary of Piraeus Bank S.A.
